each project has a status
go status means the project is approved, funded and staffed
minimal staff is a pm
minimal budget is 0
approval has to come from somewhere
somewhere is tbd

excecuting a project means it has a few things
1. an overview document
2. a schedule of milestones with key dates
3. a schedule of tasks within each milestone
4. a list of tangibles being created for the project
5. a list of people working on the project
6. a list of roles and responsibilities
7. a list of people in roles assigned to tasks

all of this could be contained in a single paragraph, or listed in detail in separate documents
